Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.65,pm4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,201)}果然还是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(511,96)}去{\c&H80FFF9&}海外{\c&HF9F8F0&}吧
